<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="iddb7f9c78-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06" identifier="/us/usc/t12/s1445"><num value="1445">§ 1445.</num><heading> Succession of Federal Home Loan Banks</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Each Federal Home Loan Bank shall have succession until dissolved by the Director under this chapter or by further act of Congress.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="iddb7f9c79-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06">(<ref href="/us/act/1932-07-22/ch522/s25">July 22, 1932, ch. 522, § 25</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/47/740">47 Stat. 740</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/101/73/tVII/s701/b/1">Pub. L. 101–73, title VII, § 701(b)(1)</ref>, (3)(A), <date date="1989-08-09">Aug. 9, 1989</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/103/412">103 Stat. 412</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/110/289/dA/tII/s1204/8">Pub. L. 110–289, div. A, title II, § 1204(8)</ref>, <date date="2008-07-30">July 30, 2008</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/122/2786">122 Stat. 2786</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
